reviewText: I'm very pleased with this VHS! I was so happy to find this little movie, I remember watching it as a kid! When it came it was still wrapped in plastic. I'll probably leave it in the plastic and keep it as a collective item.
I have watched this since I was little, I love it!!!!
The tape was old and a lot of lines in it
Plays great. Shipped very fast and my son is so thrilled with it. A must own for Disney Halloween fans!
They want to watch this video all the time. Only problem is they want to watch it all the time.
The quality of the tape was wonderful. however, i didn't receive it in time for halloween because i received it 7 Nov. oh well. the kids will like it anyway
